  After ×3: [1, 5, 7, 11, 13, 17, 19, 23, 25, 29]
  After ×5: [1, 7, 11, 13, 17, 19, 23, 29]

  Result = [1, 7, 11, 13, 17, 19, 23, 29]
  E₈ exponents = [1, 7, 11, 13, 17, 19, 23, 29]
  Match: ✓

φ(30) = 30·(1-1/2)·(1-1/3)·(1-1/5) = 30·1/2·2/3·4/5
       = 8 = rank(E₈)

Checking: rank = φ(h) for all exceptional types?
